Package: spuriouscorrelations
Title: Datasets with Strong and Spurious Correlations
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: 
    c(
        person("Tyler", "Vigen", role = c("cph")),
        person("Mauricio", "Vargas Sepulveda", role = c("aut","cre"), 
            email = "m.sepulveda@mail.utoronto.ca", 
            comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-1017-7574"))
    )
Description: Provides datasets from Vigen (2015) rescued from the Internet
    Wayback Machine. These should be preserved for statistics introductory
    courses as these make it very clear that correlation is not causation.
